<h2>Studies</h2>
<p>
    I recently graduated from the <a href="/writing/my-wisconsin-experience/">University of Wisconsin-Madison</a>, where I majored in Computer Sciences and Data Science. I spent most of my time hanging out in the
    <a href="https://upl.cs.wisc.edu/" target="_blank">UPL</a> on campus with my <a href="/friends">friends</a>.
</p>
<p>
    While there I helped organize <a href="https://www.madhacks.io/" target="_blank">MadHacks</a>, the university's hackathon. I also did some machine learning research on generative materials, and was part of the <a href="https://wqi.wisc.edu/wqcc/" target="_blank">Wisconsin Quantum Computing Club</a>.
</p>
