<h2>Colophon</h2>
<p>
    Built with <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" target="_blank">Eleventy</a> and HTML and CSS. No JavaScript by default; posts that need it pull in MathJax, a table of contents, sidenotes, or category filters. Images are converted to AVIF at build time, and links prefetch on hover via <a href="https://instant.page/" target="_blank">instant.page</a>. There's an <a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a> and a <a href="/sitemap.xml">sitemap</a>.
</p>
<p>Source <a href="https://github.com/nicosalm/salm.dev/" target="_blank">on GitHub</a>.</p>

